    "body": "I didn't know about the [`monitorEvents`](https://developers.google.com/web/tools/chrome-devtools/console/events) method. That's pretty handy.\r\n\r\nDo you see the events when you use `document.body` instead of [`$0`](https://developers.google.com/web/tools/chrome-devtools/console/command-line-reference#0_-_4)?\r\n\r\n```js\r\nmonitorEvents(document.body, 'click')\r\n```\r\n\r\n"
