    "updated_at": "2017-03-12T21:38:44Z",
    "body": "This appears to only be a bug on macOS.  After playing around in Chrome in this scenario it looks like the click event is delayed until the menu is gone and `mousedown` and `mouseup` events never get fired in this scenario.\r\n\r\nChrome probably has some haxy workaround for this but I couldn't find it in code üëç "
