    "updated_at": "2017-06-13T10:19:46Z",
    "body": "This is a behavior of macOS, the click event that cancels the menu is not passed to the application. You can probably try using the `acceptFirstMouse` option to override it.\r\n\r\nClosing as won't fix since it is a behavior of macOS."
